steps to clone(copy) my project from github...

1)open vs2013
2)go to team explorer
3)click plug icon (which is for team project located right side of home)
4)navigate "Local Git Repos" down
5)click clone 
add url as - https://github.com/vvkpr8993/HIMS.git
also save locally to your harddisk in below textbox
 hit clone..


6)after done..
open saved repos from your local machine
7) make change 
8)hit commit and push your changed code 
it may ask you your git credentials

provide uderid pwd of github.. 

done...!
